WEBVTT

step-1-intro
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.026
Welcome to Cutroom
This is Foley's Cutroom, the home base where your team reviews auto-generated product walkthrough videos.

step-2-browse_folders
00:00:06.467 --> 00:00:13.247
Browse walkthrough folders
Each folder card represents one walkthrough. You can see the step count, number of takes, and who last touched it.

step-3-open_walkthrough
00:00:13.851 --> 00:00:20.596
Open a walkthrough
Opening the Foley walkthrough brings up all five steps, each captured automatically from an incoming pull request.

step-4-review_steps
00:00:21.037 --> 00:00:27.271
Review steps and clips
Scroll down to see each step's narration text, clip preview, and timing sitting side by side.

step-5-inspect_take
00:00:27.654 --> 00:00:34.760
Inspect a take
Each take shows the recorded clip alongside its step title and narration, ready for your team to approve or re-generate.

step-6-publish_flow
00:00:35.143 --> 00:00:42.863
Approve and publish
Once the take looks right, approving it here lets Foley publish the updated video and keep your docs current automatically.
